<span class="font-bold text-brandBlue pr-4">What is GaN technology and why does it matter?</span>
<svg class="icon-chevron-down text-brandOrange shrink-0 transition-transform duration-300" viewBox="0 0 448 512" width="16"><path d="M201.4 406.6c12.5 12.5 32.8 12.5 45.3 0l192-192c12.5-12.5 12.5-32.8 0-45.3s-32.8-12.5-45.3 0L224 338.7 54.6 169.4c-12.5-12.5-32.8-12.5-45.3 0s-12.5 32.8 0 45.3l192 192z" fill="currentColor"/></svg>
</button>
<div class="hidden px-6 pb-5 text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed"><p>GaN (Gallium Nitride) is a semiconductor material that replaces traditional silicon in chargers. Benefits: 40% smaller size, 30% better heat dissipation, higher efficiency (less energy wasted as heat), and support for higher power output in compact form factors. WOWOHCOOL uses 5th generation GaN (GaN V) in our latest charger lines. <a href="/products/gan-charger" class="text-brandOrange hover:underline font-bold">Browse our GaN charger lineup</a>.</p></div>
</div>

<div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
<button onclick="this.nextElementSibling.classList.toggle('hidden');this.querySelector('svg').classList.toggle('rotate-180')" class="w-full px-6 py-5 flex items-center justify-between text-left hover:bg-slate-50 transition">
<span class="font-bold text-brandBlue pr-4">What is a semi-solid-state battery?</span>
<svg class="icon-chevron-down text-brandOrange shrink-0 transition-transform duration-300" viewBox="0 0 448 512" width="16"><path d="M201.4 406.6c12.5 12.5 32.8 12.5 45.3 0l192-192c12.5-12.5 12.5-32.8 0-45.3s-32.8-12.5-45.3 0L224 338.7 54.6 169.4c-12.5-12.5-32.8-12.5-45.3 0s-12.5 32.8 0 45.3l192 192z" fill="currentColor"/></svg>
</button>
<div class="hidden px-6 pb-5 text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed"><p>Semi-solid-state battery technology replaces the liquid electrolyte in traditional lithium-ion batteries with a gel-like solid electrolyte. Benefits: 50% thinner profile, 30% higher energy density, significantly reduced fire risk, and longer cycle life (500+ cycles). WOWOHCOOL's semi-solid-state power bank line was featured at CES 2026. <a href="/products/power-bank" class="text-brandOrange hover:underline font-bold">Explore semi-solid-state power banks</a>.</p></div>
</div>

<div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
<button onclick="this.nextElementSibling.classList.toggle('hidden');this.querySelector('svg').classList.toggle('rotate-180')" class="w-full px-6 py-5 flex items-center justify-between text-left hover:bg-slate-50 transition">
<span class="font-bold text-brandBlue pr-4">What is Qi2 wireless charging?</span>
<svg class="icon-chevron-down text-brandOrange shrink-0 transition-transform duration-300" viewBox="0 0 448 512" width="16"><path d="M201.4 406.6c12.5 12.5 32.8 12.5 45.3 0l192-192c12.5-12.5 12.5-32.8 0-45.3s-32.8-12.5-45.3 0L224 338.7 54.6 169.4c-12.5-12.5-32.8-12.5-45.3 0s-12.5 32.8 0 45.3l192 192z" fill="currentColor"/></svg>
</button>
<div class="hidden px-6 pb-5 text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed"><p>Qi2 is the latest wireless charging standard from the Wireless Power Consortium. Key feature: MPP (Magnetic Power Profile) uses N52H neodymium magnets for perfect alignment every time, ensuring 15W fast charging without the "searching for the sweet spot" frustration. Fully backwards compatible with existing Qi devices. Supports iPhone MagSafe and Android devices. <a href="/products/wireless-charger" class="text-brandOrange hover:underline font-bold">View Qi2 wireless chargers</a>.</p></div>
</div>

</div>

