<div class="hidden px-6 pb-5 text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed"><p>We take IP protection seriously. We sign NDAs and NNN (Non-Use, Non-Disclosure, Non-Circumvention) agreements. For OEM clients: your design files and specifications remain your property. For ODM: mutually agreed IP ownership terms in the contract. Molds and tooling owned by you remain under your control. We do not share client designs with third parties. For critical IP, we recommend design patent registration in China as additional protection.</p></div>
